title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Timeless
description:
The Timeless is a classic pintail carver designed for smooth, open-stance skating. It features a wide concave platform and substantial wheelbase for maximum push and speed stability.
Artist: Hunter Patrick
Artist: Justin Kious
Artist: Nanami Cowdroy
Artist: Eric Waetzig
Artist: Derek Nobbs

L: 46.00” W: 9.50” WB: 32.25”
To learn more about the Timeless visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/timeless/
